data.description:
Beautiful 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom with a flex room home in the highly sought-after Trolley Run neighborhood, just minutes from charming downtown Aiken!  

Approaching the property, you'll be greeted by a welcoming rocking chair front porch, the perfect spot to sip your morning coffee or relax in the evening. Stepping inside, you'll be immediately captivated by the bright entryway, adorned with an adjacent room featuring French doors. This space is versatile, ideal for your home office or a formal living area, allowing you to create the perfect setting for your needs.

The heart of the home beckons, with an open living area that is bathed in natural light, seamlessly flowing into a dining space that overlooks the spacious backyard. The well-appointed kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, white cabinetry, and a convenient breakfast bar. Whether you're entertaining guests or preparing family meals, this space is designed for both functionality and style.

The spacious owner's suite is a sanctuary of comfort, complete with a sitting area and a generously sized en suite bathroom. Here, you'll find a double sink vanity, a large garden tub, and a separate shower. The highlight, however, is the immense walk-in closet that provides ample storage for your wardrobe and more.

Upstairs, you'll discover additional roomy bedrooms, ideal for family members or guests. The bathroom on this level is equipped with a double sink vanity and a tub/shower combo, ensuring convenience and comfort for everyone.

For outdoor enthusiasts, the backyard is a true haven. A stunning pergola adorns the patio area, creating the perfect setting for outdoor dining, relaxation, and entertainment. The space is fenced and spacious, providing a safe and private area for play, gardening, or simply enjoying the sunset.

Don't miss this opportunity to make this exceptional property your forever home. With its ideal location, you'll enjoy the convenience of city amenities, nearby parks, and easy access to the beautiful downtown Aiken. Contact us today to schedule your private tour and make this dream home yours!
